        <li>Installed and configured Devise.</li>
        <li>Migrated in username, first_name, last_name, and roles attributes to user model.</li>
        <li>Username, first name, and last name has to be filled up during sign up form.</li>
        <li>Usernames are unique during sign up form.</li>
        <li>User has two roles; member and admin.</li>
        <li>When users register, they are defaulted to member role.</li>
        <li>Currently, there is no way to make a user admin in the web. Have to do this manually via console. Will update in the future.</li>
        <li>All user forms do not have any styling done, all just barebones. Will update them in the future.</li>
        <li>Installed simple form gem for simplicity.</li>
